name: Unalived
description:
You're death.

Not DEAD... well not quite dead, but also not alive. So aren't the people in this castle. They're been "Unalived" a long time ago. But now you need to earn that paycheck and make sure you send them off properly.

Slash your way through rooms of enemies and try get to the end as fast as possible (and brag about your time in the comments).

W/Space - Jump
A/D - Move
Left Mouse - Slash
Shift/Right Mouse - Dash

Good luck to you Reaper. Go forth and have a bountiful harvest!🌾
